trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma assinatura a um evento do timer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] TimerEventSubscription objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Objetos TimerEventSubscription são adicionados à fila de timer associada a uma instância de fluxo de trabalho para enviar uma mensagem para um determinado <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>em uma hora especificada.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Quando o tempo especificado por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>for atingido, o fluxo de trabalho do mecanismo de tempo de execução envia uma mensagem contendo o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>especificado pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: A fila de timer associada a uma instância de fluxo de trabalho está contida no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific TimerEventSubscription.
trans-unit.target: Você pode examinar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo>objetos retornados por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>para determinar quais atividades estão esperando um TimerEventSubscription específico.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>e o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService>usam assinaturas de evento de timer para fornecer a parte de sua funcionalidade.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>
